# Author: Eric Brugger
# Date:   October 27, 2000
#
# Usage:
#    visit-install-run [-<machine name>] -v <version>
#
# Modifications from visit-install-open:
#   Brad Whitlock, Tue Mar 7 14:08:59 PST 2006
